## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of up-to-date data and the inherent biases present in self-reported surveys and studies. Additionally, the rapidly evolving nature of social media platforms means that the impacts discussed may change over time as new features and platforms emerge. Further research is needed to explore the long-term effects of social media on different demographics and to develop strategies for mitigating its negative impacts while enhancing its benefits.

